messages.content: You and Daishiro  Taniguchi are celebrating 5 years of friendship on Facebook

I see

I see. its cool !! Yeah, I am planing to go back to Japan and then I will take it again.
Cool. Are you going to take the test again? I'm doing good - I'm teaching 6th grade math in Indiana. I'm planning to visit Aras soon - he lives close to Indiana.

yes, see you tomorrow !!

I arrive at 11am on Saturday. And then I'll take a taxi to town, so I could meet you in Delap in the afternoon, if you want
Hello, Andy !! I am living in Delap. Yeah, we can meet and talk !! What time will you arrive here this Saturday??

Hi Daishiro! I will arrive in Majuro on Saturday, June 16. Where do you live now? Let me know if we can meet up sometime after I arrive. I want to hear about how you've been doing. And I also want to ask some questions about teaching math - I found out that I will be teaching 2 math classes this summer for the Upward Bound summer school program.
oh, really? ok, im looking forward to seeing you.

Cool. OK, I will let you know

oh, I see. I will be here.
